<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that are moving substantially or trading  
heavily today on the New York Stock Exchange and Nasdaq Stock 
Market. 

</P>
<P>
                               *NYSE    	

</P>
<P>
	Mirage Resorts, down 2 at 14 3/4  
</P>
<P>
	The Las Vegas-based casino hotel company expects second-quarter  
earnings of 7 to 10 cents a share, below levels from a year ago and 
analysts' estimates. The company blamed results at its table games, 
the opening of its Beau Rivage resort in Biloxi, Miss., and the 
