	GoTo.com, up 11 at 48 7/16  
</P>
<P>
	The Pasadena, Calif. Internet search engine company posted  
strong June gains in the number of electronic commerce advertisers. 
And Netscape Communications said it would include a link to 
GoTo.com's Web site in an upgraded version of its popular Web 
search service. 

  	   	
