<HEADLINE> Text of Julius Erving Statement </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Text of the statement by basketball great Julius Erving, who  
said Friday he is the father of tennis player Alexandra Stevenson: 
</P>
<P>
	This is the first and only official statement I will make  
regarding my relationship with Alexandra Stevenson. 
</P>
<P>
	In response to inquiries received, I acknowledge a relationship  
with her mother in 1980. My wife (who has known from the beginning) 
and children are aware of this situation. All matters concerning 
Alexandra since her birth have been handled privately through 
counsel. 
</P>
<P>
	I am pleased to see Alexandra, at 18, doing so well and I  
applaud her mother's efforts and courage. 
</P>
</TEXT>
